# 38-Parameter Filtering Engine — Implementation Reference

> **Files changed**
> - [scripts/analysis/ai_parser.py](file:///d:/University/Semester%208th/FYP/AI/scripts/analysis/ai_parser.py) — extended NLP parser
> - [scripts/analysis/validate_model.py](file:///d:/University/Semester%208th/FYP/AI/scripts/analysis/validate_model.py) — calculation & validation engine
> - [scripts/analysis/test_parser_quick.py](file:///d:/University/Semester%208th/FYP/AI/scripts/analysis/test_parser_quick.py) — fast unit-test harness (no DB needed)

---

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["Natural Language Claim"] --> B["ai_parser.parse_claim()"]
    B --> |LLM available| C["Gemini gemini-2.5-flash"]
    B --> |No API key| D["Rule-based _mock_parse()"]
    C --> E["Structured JSON (38 filters)"]
    D --> E
    E --> F["validate_model.validate_claim()"]
    F --> G["IdentityEngine.resolve_for_ingestion()"]
    G --> H["apply_filters() — 38-dim filter"]
    H --> I["_batting_metrics() / _bowling_metrics()"]
    I --> J["Truth-O-Meter Verdict"]
```

---

## The 38 Parameters

### Match Context (1–12)

| # | Key | Type | Example value |
|---|-----|------|---------------|
| 1 | `venue_name` | str | `"Melbourne Cricket Ground"` |
| 2 | [city](file:///d:/University/Semester%208th/FYP/AI/scripts/analysis/validate_model.py#65-67) | str | `"Melbourne"` |
| 3 | [country](file:///d:/University/Semester%208th/FYP/AI/scripts/analysis/validate_model.py#65-67) | str | `"Australia"` |
| 4 | `format` | str | `"Test"`, `"ODI"`, `"T20I"`, `"T20"` |
| 5 | `season` | str | `"2022"`, `"2019/20"` |
| 6 | `day_night` | str | `"Day"`, `"Night"`, `"Day/Night"` |
| 7 | `toss_winner` | str | team name |
| 8 | `toss_decision` | str | `"bat"` or `"field"` |
| 9 | `innings` | int | `1`, `2`, `3`, `4` |
| 10 | `series` | str | `"Ashes"`, `"Asia Cup"` |
| 11 | `home_away` | str | `"Home"`, `"Away"` |
| 12 | `neutral_venue` | bool | `true` / `false` |

### Batting Analytics (13–25)

| # | Key / Metric | Notes |
|---|-------------|-------|
| 13 | `subject` (batter) | Resolved via IdentityEngine |
| 14 | `Total Runs` | `runs_batter.sum()` |
| 15 | `Balls Faced` | row count of deliveries |
| 16 | `Batting Average` | `runs / dismissals` |
| 17 | `Strike Rate` | [(runs / balls) × 100](file:///d:/University/Semester%208th/FYP/AI/scripts/pipeline/cricsheet_ingestion_engine.py#255-298) |
| 18 | `dismissal_type` | filter by `wicket_type` column |
| 19 | `Dot Ball %` | [(balls where runs_batter==0) / balls × 100](file:///d:/University/Semester%208th/FYP/AI/scripts/pipeline/cricsheet_ingestion_engine.py#255-298) |
| 20 | `Boundary %` | [(balls where runs_batter in [4,6]) / balls × 100](file:///d:/University/Semester%208th/FYP/AI/scripts/pipeline/cricsheet_ingestion_engine.py#255-298) |
| 21 | `batting_position` | filter by `batting_position` column |
| 22 | `non_striker` | filter by `non_striker` column (resolved) |
| 23 | `Partnership Runs` | aggregated `runs_batter` per partnership segment |
| 24 | `High Score` | max innings total across `match_id + innings` |
| 25 | `Milestones` | count innings ≥ 50 or ≥ 100 |

### Bowling & Matchup Analytics (26–38)

| # | Key / Metric | Notes |
|---|-------------|-------|
| 26 | [bowler](file:///d:/University/Semester%208th/FYP/AI/scripts/analysis/validate_model.py#69-95) / `batter_vs_bowler` | specific bowler filter (identity-resolved) |
| 27 | `bowler_type` | `"Spin"` / `"Pace"` from bowlers.csv + IdentityEngine |
| 28 | `bowler_hand` | `"Left"` / `"Right"` from IdentityEngine bowlingstyle field |
| 29 | `Economy Rate` | `runs_total / overs_bowled` |
| 30 | `Bowling Strike Rate` | `balls_bowled / wickets` |
| 31 | `Wickets` | `is_bowler_wicket.sum()` |
| 32 | `Dots Forced` | rows where `runs_total == 0` |
| 33 | `Extras Conceded` | sum of wides + noballs + byes + legbyes |
| 34 | `over_number` | 0-indexed over filter |
| 35 | [match_phase](file:///d:/University/Semester%208th/FYP/AI/scripts/analysis/validate_model.py#97-104) | `"Powerplay"` (overs 0–5), `"Middle"` (6–14), `"Death"` (15+) |
| 36 | `batter_vs_bowler_type` | e.g. `"Leg-spin"`, `"Left-arm Pace"` |
| 37 | `batter_vs_bowler` | specific bowler head-to-head |
| 38 | `Runs Conceded in Over` | `runs_total.sum()` after over-level filter |

